<lb n="0741b17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0741b18" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1028A</cb:docNumber><cb:div type="jing">
<lb n="0741b19" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0741004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，【甲】天平時代寫越前西福寺藏本，【乙】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本</note>佛說護諸童子陀羅<note n="0741005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尼＋（呪）【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0741005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尼【大】，尼呪【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0741005"><lem wit="【大】">尼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">尼呪</rdg></app>經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0741b20" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0741b21" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0741006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔元魏天竺〕－【甲】</note><note n="0741006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">元魏天竺【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0741006"><lem wit="【大】">元魏<note n="0741007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔天竺〕－【三】</note><note n="0741007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天竺【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0741007"><lem wit="【大】">天竺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>三<note n="0741008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">藏＋（法師）【三】</note><note n="0741008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">藏【大】，藏法師【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0741008"><lem wit="【大】">藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">藏法師</rdg></app>菩提<note n="0741009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">流＝留【三】【乙】</note><note n="0741009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">流【大】，留【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0741009"><lem wit="【大】">流</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">留</rdg></app>支譯</byline>
<lb n="0741b22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0741b2201">爾時如來初成正覺。有一大梵天王。來詣佛
<lb n="0741b23" ed="T"/>所敬禮佛足。而作是言。</p>
<lb n="0741b24" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT19p0741b2401"><l>南無佛陀耶</l><l>南無達摩耶</l>
<lb n="0741b25" ed="T"/><l>南無僧伽耶</l><l>我禮佛<note n="0741010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">世＝足【三】【甲】</note><note n="0741010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世【大】，足【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0741010"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">足</rdg></app>尊</l>
<lb n="0741b26" ed="T"/><l>照世大法王</l><l>在於閻浮提</l>
<lb n="0741b27" ed="T"/><l>最初說神呪</l><l>甘露淨勝法</l>
<lb n="0741b28" ed="T"/><l>及禮無著僧</l><l>已禮牟尼足</l>
<lb n="0741b29" ed="T"/><l>即時說偈言</l><l>世尊諸如來</l>
<pb n="0741c" xml:id="T19.1028A.0741c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0741c01" ed="T"/><l>聲聞及辟支</l><l>諸仙護世王</l>
<lb n="0741c02" ed="T"/><l>大力龍天神</l><l>如是等諸眾</l>
<lb n="0741c03" ed="T"/><l>皆於人中生</l><l>有夜叉羅剎</l>
<lb n="0741c04" ed="T"/><l>常憙噉人胎</l><l>非人王境界</l>
<lb n="0741c05" ed="T"/><l>強力所不制</l><l>能令人無子</l>
<lb n="0741c06" ed="T"/><l>傷害於胞胎</l><l>男女交會時</l>
<lb n="0741c07" ed="T"/><l>使其意迷亂</l><l>懷<note n="0741011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">任＝妊【三】【乙】</note><note n="0741011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">任【大】，妊【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0741011"><lem wit="【大】">任</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">妊</rdg></app>不成就</l>
<lb n="0741c08" ed="T"/><l>或歌羅安<note n="0741012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">浮＝陀【三】</note><note n="0741012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">浮【大】，陀【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0741012"><lem wit="【大】">浮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">陀</rdg></app></l><l>無子以傷胎</l>
<lb n="0741c09" ed="T"/><l>及生時奪命</l><l><note n="0741013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔皆是諸惡鬼〕－【甲】</note><note n="0741013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皆是諸惡鬼【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0741013"><lem wit="【大】">皆是諸惡鬼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0741c10" ed="T"/><l>為其作嬈害</l><l>我今說彼名</l>
<lb n="0741c11" ed="T"/><l>願佛聽我說</l></lg>
<lb n="0741c12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0741c1201">第一名彌酬迦　第二名彌伽王　第三名騫
<lb n="0741c13" ed="T"/>陀　第四名阿波悉魔羅　第五名牟致迦
<lb n="0741c14" ed="T"/>　第六名魔致迦　第七名<note n="0741014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">閻＝闍ヵ【乙】＊</note><note n="0741014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">閻【大】＊，闍【考偽-乙】＊</note><app n="0741014"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">閻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="correctionRemark">闍</rdg></app>彌迦　第八名迦
<lb n="0741c15" ed="T"/>彌尼　第九名<note n="0741015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">黎＝梨【三】【乙】＊</note><note n="0741015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">黎【大】＊，梨【宋】【元】【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0741015"><lem wit="【大】">黎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">梨</rdg></app><note n="0741016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">婆＝波【三】【乙】＊</note><note n="0741016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婆【大】＊，波【宋】【元】【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0741016"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">波</rdg></app>坻　第十名富多那
<lb n="0741c16" ed="T"/>　第十一名曼多難提　第十二名舍究尼　第
<lb n="0741c17" ed="T"/>十三名揵吒波尼<note n="0741017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔尼〕－【乙】</note><note n="0741017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尼【大】，〔－〕【乙】</note><app n="0741017"><lem wit="【大】">尼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>　第十四名目佉曼荼
<lb n="0741c18" ed="T"/>　第十五名藍婆</p>
<lb n="0741c19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0741c1901">此十五鬼神。常遊行世間。為嬰孩小兒。而作
<lb n="0741c20" ed="T"/>於恐怖。我今當說此諸鬼神恐怖形相。以此
<lb n="0741c21" ed="T"/>形相。令諸小兒皆生驚畏。</p>
<lb n="0741c22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0741c2201">彌酬迦者其形如牛。</p>
<lb n="0741c23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0741c2301">彌迦王者其形如師子。</p>
<lb n="0741c24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0741c2401">騫陀者其形如鳩魔<note n="0741018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔羅〕－【甲】</note><note n="0741018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">羅【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0741018"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>天。</p>
<lb n="0741c25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0741c2501">阿波悉魔羅者其形如野狐。</p>
<lb n="0741c26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0741c2601">牟致迦者其形如獼猴。</p>
<lb n="0741c27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0741c2701">魔致迦者其形如羅剎女。</p>
<lb n="0741c28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0741c2801"><anchor xml:id="fxT19p0741c01"/>閻彌迦者其形如馬。</p>
<lb n="0741c29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0741c2901">迦彌尼者其形如婦女。</p>
<pb n="0742a" xml:id="T19.1028A.0742a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0742a01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a0101"><app type="star" corresp="#0741015"><lem wit="【大】">黎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">梨</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0741016"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">波</rdg></app>坻者其形如狗。</p>
<lb n="0742a02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a0201">富多那者其形如猪。</p>
<lb n="0742a03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a0301">曼多難提者其形如猫兒。</p>
<lb n="0742a04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a0401"><note n="0742001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">舍＝金【甲】</note><note n="0742001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">舍【大】，金【甲】</note><app n="0742001"><lem wit="【大】">舍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">金</rdg></app>究尼者其形如<note n="0742002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鳥＝烏【三】【乙】</note><note n="0742002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鳥【大】，烏【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0742002"><lem wit="【大】">鳥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">烏</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0742a05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a0501"><note n="0742003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">乾＝揵【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0742003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乾【大】＊，揵【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0742003"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">揵</rdg></app>吒<app type="star" corresp="#0741016"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">波</rdg></app>尼尼者其形如<note n="0742004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">雉＝鷄【三】【乙】</note><note n="0742004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">雉【大】，鷄【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0742004"><lem wit="【大】">雉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">鷄</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0742a06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a0601">目佉曼荼者其形如<note n="0742005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">獯＝熏【三】</note><note n="0742005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">獯【大】，熏【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0742005"><lem wit="【大】">獯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">熏</rdg></app>狐。</p>
<lb n="0742a07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a0701">藍婆者其形如蛇。</p>
<lb n="0742a08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a0801">此十五鬼。神著諸小兒令其驚怖。我今當<note n="0742006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">復＝與【三】【乙】</note><note n="0742006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復【大】，與【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0742006"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">與</rdg></app>
<lb n="0742a09" ed="T"/>說諸小兒怖畏之相。</p>
<lb n="0742a10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a1001">彌酬迦鬼<note n="0742007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">者著＝著者【三】＊</note><note n="0742007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者著【大】＊，著者【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0742007"><lem wit="【大】">者著</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">著者</rdg></app>小兒眼睛迴轉。</p>
<lb n="0742a11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a1101">彌<note n="0742008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">迦＝伽【乙】</note><note n="0742008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">迦【大】，伽【乙】</note><app n="0742008"><lem wit="【大】">迦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">伽</rdg></app>王鬼<app type="star" corresp="#0742007"><lem wit="【大】">者著</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">著者</rdg></app>小兒數數嘔吐。</p>
<lb n="0742a12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a1201">騫陀鬼<app type="star" corresp="#0742007"><lem wit="【大】">者著</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">著者</rdg></app>小兒其兩肩動。</p>
<lb n="0742a13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a1301">阿波悉魔羅鬼<app type="star" corresp="#0742007"><lem wit="【大】">者著</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">著者</rdg></app>小兒口中<note n="0742009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">沫＝味【甲】</note><note n="0742009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沫【大】，味【甲】</note><app n="0742009"><lem wit="【大】">沫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">味</rdg></app>出。</p>
<lb n="0742a14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a1401">牟致迦鬼<app type="star" corresp="#0742007"><lem wit="【大】">者著</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">著者</rdg></app>小兒把<note n="0742010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">捲＝拳【三】【乙】</note><note n="0742010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">捲【大】，拳【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0742010"><lem wit="【大】">捲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">拳</rdg></app>不展。</p>
<lb n="0742a15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a1501">魔致迦鬼<app type="star" corresp="#0742007"><lem wit="【大】">者著</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">著者</rdg></app>小兒自齧其舌。</p>
