<lb n="0742a17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a1701">迦彌尼鬼<app type="star" corresp="#0742007"><lem wit="【大】">者著</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">著者</rdg></app>小兒<note n="0742011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">樂＋（喜）【甲】</note><note n="0742011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">樂【大】，樂喜【甲】</note><app n="0742011"><lem wit="【大】">樂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">樂喜</rdg></app>著女人。</p>
<lb n="0742a18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a1801"><app type="star" corresp="#0741015"><lem wit="【大】">黎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">梨</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0741016"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">波</rdg></app>坻鬼<app type="star" corresp="#0742007"><lem wit="【大】">者著</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">著者</rdg></app>小兒<note n="0742012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">見＝現【三】【乙】</note><note n="0742012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見【大】，現【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0742012"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">現</rdg></app>種種雜<note n="0742013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">相＝想【甲】</note><note n="0742013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">相【大】，想【甲】</note><app n="0742013"><lem wit="【大】">相</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">想</rdg></app>。</p>
