<lb n="0742a20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a2001">曼多難提鬼者著小<note n="0742014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">兒＋（眠中）【三】</note><note n="0742014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">兒【大】，兒眠中【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0742014"><lem wit="【大】">兒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">兒眠中</rdg></app>憙啼喜笑。</p>
<lb n="0742a21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a2101"><note n="0742015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">金＝舍【三】【乙】</note><note n="0742015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">金【大】，舍【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0742015"><lem wit="【大】">金</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">舍</rdg></app>究尼鬼者著小兒不肯飲乳。</p>
<lb n="0742a22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a2201"><app type="star" corresp="#0742003"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">揵</rdg></app>吒波尼尼鬼<app type="star" corresp="#0742007"><lem wit="【大】">者著</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">著者</rdg></app>小兒咽喉聲塞。</p>
<lb n="0742a23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a2301">目佉曼荼鬼<app type="star" corresp="#0742007"><lem wit="【大】">者著</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">著者</rdg></app>小兒時氣熱病下痢。</p>
<lb n="0742a24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a2401">藍婆鬼<app type="star" corresp="#0742007"><lem wit="【大】">者著</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">著者</rdg></app>小兒數<note n="0742016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">數噫＝噫數【三】【乙】，數【甲】</note><note n="0742016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">數噫【大】，噫數【宋】【元】【明】【乙】，數【甲】</note><app n="0742016"><lem wit="【大】">數噫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">噫數</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">數</rdg></app>噦。</p>
<lb n="0742a25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742a2501">此十五鬼神。以如是等形。怖諸小兒。及其小
<lb n="0742a26" ed="T"/>兒驚怖之相。我皆已說。復有大鬼神王。名栴
<lb n="0742a27" ed="T"/>檀乾闥婆於諸鬼神最為上首。當以五色綖。
<lb n="0742a28" ed="T"/>誦此陀羅尼一遍一結。作一百<note n="0742017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔八〕－【甲】</note><note n="0742017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">八【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0742017"><lem wit="【大】">八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>結。并書其
<lb n="0742a29" ed="T"/>鬼神名字。使人齎此書綖。語彼使言。汝今疾
<pb n="0742b" xml:id="T19.1028A.0742b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0742b01" ed="T"/>去<note n="0742018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">急＝行【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0742018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">急【大】，行【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0742018"><lem wit="【大】">急</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">行</rdg></app>速如風到於四方。隨彼十五鬼神所住
<lb n="0742b02" ed="T"/>之處。與栴檀乾闥婆大鬼神王。令以五色<note n="0742019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">線＝綖【三】【乙】，縛【甲】</note><note n="0742019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">線【大】，綖【宋】【元】【明】【乙】，縛【甲】</note><app n="0742019"><lem wit="【大】">線</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">綖</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>
<lb n="0742b03" ed="T"/>縛彼鬼神<note n="0742020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔勿嬈眾生〕－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0742020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">勿嬈眾生【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0742020"><lem wit="【大】">勿嬈眾生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。兼以種種美味飲食香
<lb n="0742b04" ed="T"/>華燈明。及以乳粥供養神王。</p>
<lb n="0742b05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742b0501">爾時。大梵天王。復白佛言。世尊若有女人不
<lb n="0742b06" ed="T"/>生男女。或在胎中失壞墮落。或生已奪命。此
<lb n="0742b07" ed="T"/>諸女等欲求子息保命長壽者。<note n="0742021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">常當＝當常【三】</note><note n="0742021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常當【大】，當常【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0742021"><lem wit="【大】">常當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">當常</rdg></app>繫念修
<lb n="0742b08" ed="T"/>行善法。於月八日十五日受持八戒。清淨洗
<lb n="0742b09" ed="T"/>浴著新淨衣。禮十方佛至於中夜。取少芥子
<lb n="0742b10" ed="T"/>置已頂上。誦我所說陀羅尼呪者。令此女人
<lb n="0742b11" ed="T"/>即得如願。所生童子安隱無患。盡其形壽終
<lb n="0742b12" ed="T"/>不中夭。若有鬼神不<note n="0742022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">順＝慎【甲】</note><note n="0742022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">順【大】，慎【甲】</note><app n="0742022"><lem wit="【大】">順</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">慎</rdg></app>我呪者。我當令其頭
<lb n="0742b13" ed="T"/>破<note n="0742023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">作＝為【三】【乙】</note><note n="0742023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">作【大】，為【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0742023"><lem wit="【大】">作</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">為</rdg></app>七分<note n="0742024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔如阿梨樹枝〕－【甲】</note><note n="0742024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如阿梨樹枝【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0742024"><lem wit="【大】">如阿梨樹枝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。即說<note n="0742025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔護諸童子〕－【甲】</note><note n="0742025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">護諸童子【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0742025"><lem wit="【大】">護諸童子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>陀
<lb n="0742b14" ed="T"/>羅尼呪。</p>
<lb n="0742b15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742b1501" cb:type="dharani"><note n="0742026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">多<g ref="#CB02977"/>＝多緻【宋】＊</note><note n="0742026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">多<g ref="#CB02977"/>【大】＊，多緻【宋】＊</note><app n="0742026"><lem wit="【大】">多<g ref="#CB02977"/></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">多緻</rdg></app>他　阿伽羅　伽甯　<note n="0742027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">那＝耶【宋】</note><note n="0742027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">那【大】，耶【宋】</note><app n="0742027"><lem wit="【大】">那</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">耶</rdg></app>伽　伽甯
<lb n="0742b16" ed="T"/>　婆漏隷　秖隷　伽婆隷　婆隷　<note n="0742028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（婆隷不隷）＋不【三】【乙】</note><note n="0742028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不【大】，婆隷不隷不【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0742028"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">婆隷不隷不</rdg></app>隷　羅
<lb n="0742b17" ed="T"/>扠禰　修羅俾　遮羅<note n="0742029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">俾＋（婆陀尼）【三】【乙】，（娑尼）ィ【乙】</note><note n="0742029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">俾【大】，俾婆陀尼【宋】【元】【明】【乙】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->俾娑尼【校異-乙】</note><app n="0742029"><lem wit="【大】">俾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">俾婆陀尼</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark">俾娑尼</rdg></app>　<note n="0742030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">娑＝沙【三】，婆陀【甲】，娑尼波羅呵＝婆囉呵沙尼ィ【乙】</note><note n="0742030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">娑尼波羅呵【大】，婆囉呵沙尼【校異-乙】，沙尼波羅呵【宋】【元】【明】，婆陀尼波羅呵【甲】</note><app n="0742030"><lem wit="【大】">娑尼　<note n="0742031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">波羅＝婆囉【三】【乙】</note><note n="0742031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">波羅【大】，婆囉【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0742031"><lem wit="【大】">波羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">婆囉</rdg></app>呵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark">婆囉呵沙尼</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">沙尼波羅呵</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">婆陀尼波羅呵</rdg></app>
<lb n="0742b18" ed="T"/>　<note n="0742032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔沙尼〕－【三】【乙】</note><note n="0742032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沙尼【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0742032"><lem wit="【大】">沙尼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>　那易　彌那易　<note n="0742033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">穌＝蘇【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0742033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">穌【大】＊，蘇【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0742033"><lem wit="【大】">穌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">蘇</rdg></app><note n="0742034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">婆＝波【三】</note><note n="0742034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婆【大】，波【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0742034"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">波</rdg></app>呵</p>
<lb n="0742b19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742b1901">世尊我今說此陀羅尼呪護諸童子。令得安
<lb n="0742b20" ed="T"/>隱獲其長壽故。</p>
<lb n="0742b21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742b2101">爾時世尊一切種智。即說呪曰。</p>
<lb n="0742b22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742b2201" cb:type="dharani"><app type="star" corresp="#0742026"><lem wit="【大】">多<g ref="#CB02977"/></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">多緻</rdg></app>他　菩陀菩陀　菩陀㝹摩帝　菩提
<lb n="0742b23" ed="T"/>菩提　摩隷　式叉夜　婆舍利　婆多禰
<lb n="0742b24" ed="T"/>　婆羅陀　頭隷　頭隷　婆臘多頭隷　舍摩
<lb n="0742b25" ed="T"/>膩　<note n="0742035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">收隷＝扠鞞扠隷婆臈帝扠藍舍彌帝槃他槃絺【三】【乙】</note><note n="0742035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">收隷【大】，扠鞞扠隷婆臈帝扠藍舍彌帝槃他槃絺【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0742035"><lem wit="【大】">收隷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">扠鞞扠隷婆臈帝扠藍舍彌帝槃他槃絺</rdg></app>　婆呵膩　<note n="0742036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（祇摩膩）＋陀【三】</note><note n="0742036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">陀【大】，祇摩膩陀【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0742036"><lem wit="【大】">陀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">祇摩膩陀</rdg></app>波膩　穌婆呵
<lb n="0742b26" ed="T"/>　<anchor xml:id="fxT19p0742b02"/>膩婆羅膩　<app type="star" corresp="#0742033"><lem wit="【大】">穌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">蘇</rdg></app>婆呵</p>
<lb n="0742b27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0742b2701">此十五鬼神常食<note n="0742037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">血肉＝肉血【三】</note><note n="0742037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">血肉【大】，肉血【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0742037"><lem wit="【大】">血肉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">肉血</rdg></app>。以此陀羅尼呪力故。
<lb n="0742b28" ed="T"/>悉皆遠離不生惡心。令諸童子離於恐怖安
<lb n="0742b29" ed="T"/>隱無患。處胎初生無諸患難。誦此呪者。或於
<pb n="0742c" xml:id="T19.1028A.0742c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0742c01" ed="T"/>城邑聚落隨其住處。亦能令彼嬰孩小兒。長
<lb n="0742c02" ed="T"/>得安隱終保年壽。南無佛陀成就此呪。護諸
<lb n="0742c03" ed="T"/>童子不為諸惡鬼神之所嬈害。一切諸難一
<lb n="0742c04" ed="T"/>切恐怖。悉皆遠離<app type="star" corresp="#0742033"><lem wit="【大】">穌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">蘇</rdg></app>婆呵。時此梵天聞說此
<lb n="0742c05" ed="T"/><note n="0742038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">經歡欣＝呪歡喜【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0742038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經歡欣【大】，呪歡喜【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0742038"><lem wit="【大】">經歡欣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">呪歡喜</rdg></app>奉<note n="0742039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此下宋本有乞夢陀羅尼呪誦一百八遍誦呪訖已頭東向眠南無匐伽婆帝阿池多耶多緻他須留須留利毘利彌利彌利娑婆呵</note><note n="0742039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">行【大】，行乞夢陀羅尼呪誦一百八遍誦呪訖已頭東向眠南無匐伽婆帝阿池多耶多緻他須留須留利毘利彌利彌利娑婆呵【宋】</note><app n="0742039"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">行乞夢陀羅尼呪誦一百八遍誦呪訖已頭東向眠南無匐伽婆帝阿池多耶多緻他須留須留利毘利彌利彌利娑婆呵</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0742c06" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>佛說護諸童子<note n="0742040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔陀羅尼〕－【宋】</note><note n="0742040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">陀羅尼【大】，〔－〕【宋】</note><app n="0742040"><lem wit="【大】">陀羅<note n="0742041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尼＋（呪）【元】【明】【乙】</note><note n="0742041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尼【大】，尼呪【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0742041"><lem wit="【大】">尼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【乙】">尼呪</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>經<note n="0742042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">乙本奧書云元祿十六年三月二十八日以淨嚴和上之本再校了尊教</note><anchor type="circle"/></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
